"  Pesto:","3 cups packed fresh basil","1 cup packed fresh parsley","3  garlic cloves, chopped","1 tablespoon lemon juice","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon pepper","1/3 cup pine nuts, toasted","1/2 cup olive oil","1/2 cup grated Parmesan","  Salad:","1 pound gemelli or other short pasta","1 cup plain 2 percent Greek yogurt","2  pints cherry or grape tomatoes, halved"